  <section>
    <h1>We are a worker cooperative</h1>
    <p>
      Worker cooperatives, as defined by the Tech Co-op Network, are "businesses owned and democratically controlled
      by" their workers. As a democratically controlled business, we network with other like-minded
      groups. We are members of:
    </p>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="membership column">
        <%= image_tag "usfwc.png" %>
        <h4><%= link_to "United States Federation of Worker Coops", "http://usworker.coop/", target: "_blank" %></h4>
        <p>A network of democratically-owned businesses in the United States.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="membership column">
        <%= image_tag "natechcoop.ico" %>
        <h4><%= link_to "Tech Co-op Network", "http://techworker.coop/", target: "_blank" %></h4>
        <p>A network of North American worker cooperatives focused on technology.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>As our logo reflects, we are based in Michigan helping to bring life back into our home.</p>
  </section>

